view

Class TabsPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.TabsPane

  • public class TabsPane
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will serve as the Facade Class that contains all Panes. Using this class will allow the controller to choose which Panes show up depending on the user that loged in. All panes are added to tabs. The tabs can then be switched about.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Caio Eugenio
